Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A dragon graveyard?\N--No! It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu said going back to\Nhis nest would make him better!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be a graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu was a lost Millennial Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was all alone, for a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:02:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he made friends with you, Apis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said out of the\N1,000 years he was alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this last year with you was his happiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... You understand\Nthe dragons' language?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just somehow know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, talk about half-baked...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a liar, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the dragons' nest...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've made it back to the dragons' nest,\Nthen open your eyes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu wasn't lying at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that Millennial Dragons\Nreturn to the nest every 1,000 years
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are reborn again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A baby Millennial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An Angry Showdown!\NCross the Red Line!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I very nearly drowned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at this beautiful radiance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it marvelous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all Dragonite,\Nthe legendary elixir of immortality!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But breaking these\Nfossilized Millennial Dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,won't produce anything usable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is more than enough\Nlive Dragonite here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say? A pointless\Nfight would only be tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we make a deal\Nto split this treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do you not want eternal life?!\N--Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lie! There's no one\Nwho's not afraid of dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of us may have Devil Fruit powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a pirate's life is always\Nonly inches from death!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can't be afraid of dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. He's the kind of guy who'd\Ndie smiling doing what he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sit there and watch\Nas I take my Dragonite and leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be reckless, Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's reckless,\NI have to protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very important place\Nfor the Millennial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect this\Nplace forever and ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you insist on defying me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you can all die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sickle-Sickle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Whirlwind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But, Luffy!\N--I promised him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine staying here?!\NWhat kind of wimpiness is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't accomplished your goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to going to your nest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up by saying\Nyou're staying here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will! Don't worry about Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sickle-Sickle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...Whirlwind!\N--...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hit me, rubber man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Are my wind slashes\Nsharp enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run or hide wherever you want,\Nthere's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how will you dodge this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's pretty tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Luffy in trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sickle-Sickle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Wind Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapid Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:07:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna run or hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Go ahead and get chopped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is this?!\N--Creatures like this really exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't just a legend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose this place'll\Nsink again after a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it does, will the Millennial\NDragons leave the island, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I guess that baby Millennial\NDragon will fly off somewhere too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you have some of my\Nspecial pork buns before you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Thank you! But that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta get back to our\Njourney right away! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do? I wanna eat some pork--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just take the recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd only take three days\Nto prepare them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell you about the royal\Nfamily of Lost Island in the mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already heard about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Set sail for the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis. Want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made friends with you all,\Nand I would like to go with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm going to stay on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna learn all sorts of\Ncustoms from Grandpa Bokuden
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and protect the dragons' nest just\Nlike my ancestors did before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wait for the baby dragons\Nto come back here someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those baby dragons won't\Nbe back for another... uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Another thousand years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Don't be so cynical!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get to see the\Ndragons all grown up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure my kids' kids will get to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to keep protecting\Nthis dragon nest forever and ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys kept doing\Ncrazy stuff too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis! Never forget about Usopp-sama,\Nthe brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye! Take care, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See ya, Apis!\N--Bye! So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Apis really gonna be\Nokay all by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Apis will keep the nest safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be little,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's got twice the energy\Nand motivation of a normal person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:11:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you didn't\Nwant to go with them, Apis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd only get in the way if I went with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, now I have\Nsomething I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty reckless too,\Nbut until I met Luffy and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I would've felt like\NI could protect this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Lost Island was just\Na story and that it didn't exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Luffy and the others took\NGrandpa Ryu on a search for it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without even doubting its\Nexistence in the slightest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that they taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that if you never give up on\Nyour dreams and try your hardest,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your wishes just may come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone worked so hard and\Nrisked their lives for their friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who all had a heart-to-heart connection!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm one of their friends, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:12:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to try my hardest, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say? Will you help me with my dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! Let's try our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! If you're going\Nto protect Lost Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll need to know about your ancestors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, there was the first king...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've already had enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Apis! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to know about these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:13:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! I have a report of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see big rain clouds up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a storm under 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're back\Non our original course...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be seeing the\NRed Line at any time now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Line, at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji! We're finally going!\NWe're finally going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sowwy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it really like how it's drawn here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard the rumors about it,\Nand it's drawn on this map, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it really is true, then the entrance\Nto the Grand Line is a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We gotta crash into a mountain?\N--You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't believe it myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the map has canals\Nthat lead to the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might mean we have to go up it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there are canals or whatever,\Na ship can't climb up a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what the map says!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Nami-san would never\Nsay anything that's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stole that map from Buggy, right?\NCan we really trust it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Someone help with the rudder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-kun! Give Usopp a hand!\N--It won't budge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can't think with all his shouting!\N--It won't move! Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Doesn't this current\Nseem a bit strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Usopp! What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"D-Doesn't this current\Nseem a bit strong?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Current...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's it!\N--That's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really do go up the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still saying that stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? The guiding light was\Ndefinitely pointing to here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the Red Line... Reverse Mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Little help over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See these canals here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If major currents from the four oceans\Nall flow toward this mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the four currents would go up\Nthese canals, collide at the top,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then flow into the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Mountain is a "winter island,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So any currents that\Ncollide into the Red Line
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will plummet from the\Nsurface into the depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we screw up and miss\Nthe entrance to the canal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Going Merry will run smack\Ninto the Red Line's rock face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and get wrecked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then we'd be at the bottom\Nof the ocean. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, basically, it's a mystery mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe you don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, now that we're on this current,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we don't\Nmess up with the rudder,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should be able to go straight\Nto the summit of Reverse Mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! You're so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:16:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of ships\Ngoing over mountains before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard some stuff before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stories about the mystery mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that half of everyone\Nwho heads to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dies before entering it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew getting in wouldn't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-kun! Could you get the sail?\N--Yes, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy! Help out!\N--Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I see the mystery mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's insanely huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance to the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the Red Line, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:17:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I can't see the top\Nbecause of the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting sucked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hold the rudder good!\N--We're on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami! Where's the entrance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crash into the rocks\Nif we keep going this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crack in that cliff...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Keep going straight ahead!\N--A-Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Is that the canal entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The damn ocean really is\Nflowing up the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta make our way through\Nthose water gates just right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise the ship'll\Nbe busted into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're getting off course!\NMore to the right! Right! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The right?! Go starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rudder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:19:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's just a straight shot to the summit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I wanna see! I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm unstuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let me see, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--It's the Sicko Fruit guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You!\N--You're still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What tiny eyes!\N--Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse the whole lot of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, my dream of\NDragonite has been crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just leave things as they are now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I'll have\Nyour 30 million-Berry head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just surrender to your fate\Nlike a good little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he uses his wind slashes here,\Nthere's no telling what he'll rip apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't act carelessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that?!\NYou can't lay a finger on me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Dragonite!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Good thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't swim either, so I don't\Nthink he'll be following us any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given this current, being able\Nto swim wouldn't matter anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:21:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're above the clouds now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The summit! It's the summit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do what Mihawk said...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To find the All Blue there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To draw my perfect sea charts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prove I'm a brave warrior of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the greatest sea\Nin the world! The Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The One Piece is up ahead, somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.56,0:22:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! I see a mountain up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be! It should be\Nnothing but ocean up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A black wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.08,0:24:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! We gotta do\Nsomething before we crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No! This is...!\N--A whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whale?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.09,0:24:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The First Line of Defense?\NThe Giant Whale Laboon Appears"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.53,0:24:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
